consider Q being set such that A10: Q in (the carrier of R) and A11: y = ( Class (E,Q) ) by EQREL_1:def 3;
reconsider P,Q as (Element of R) by A8,A10;
( Class (E,( P * Q )) ) is (Element of A) by EQREL_1:def 3;
