end;
consider h being (BinOp of A) such that A12: (for a,b being (Element of A) holds R[ a,b,( h . (a,b) ) ]) from BINOP_1:sch 3(A7);
take doubleLoopStr (# A,g,h,u,z #);
thus thesis by A6,A12;
